The process for pushing a new version is too complicated and
manual. 

* Update HISTORY
* Touch the new version number whenever its used. 
   (Should only be in the project files.)
* Rake fresh
* bin/version 1.2.0 <midje-version>
* bin/run-tests
* Rake fresh
* bin/version 1.1.0 <midje-version>
* bin/run-tests

* Rake fresh
* Rake upload
* DO NOT CLEAN.
* bin/gather-downloads
* Commit
* git tag -a -m "message" v.x.x.x   ;; git push --tags
* Push to github

* Update example page, if needed.
* Try out downloads.
